{"tid":260727,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"柯達手機正式開售　主打拍照售價3120元 (22:01)","createTime":"2017-05-27T23:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T08:00:52.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6d8ea0c9bceaa9fa67e4ae38da67f5bf62508340","tid":260727,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T23:45:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170527/img/20170527220151fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170527%2Fimg%2F20170527220151fi_p1.jpg&h=f3636188&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n柯達首款智能手機Ektra。<br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=weW6yIUZoGcZx37EmzOfSmowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=87848a03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】外媒報道，去年底，柯達正式發布旗下的首款智能手機Ektra，它的名字是為了紀念75年前的經典相機產品。<br />\n<br />\nEktra搭載一顆碩大的2100萬像素攝像頭，F/2.0光圈，支持光學防抖、相位對焦、4K視頻錄製，雙色溫閃光燈，前置1300萬自拍鏡頭。<br />\n<br />\n基本配置上，Ektra擁有5寸1080P顯示屏，Helio X20處理器，3GB RAM，32GB ROM，支持microSD卡擴展，3000mAh電池。<br />\n<br />\n外形方面，柯達在機身右側設計了實體拍照鍵，書卷式&ldquo;下巴&rdquo;，雖然後殼看起來是皮革，邊框看起來是金屬，但實際都是塑料。<br />\n<br />\n目前，新機已經在柯達官網開賣，定價399.99美元(約3,120港元)。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170527/20170527220151fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170527%2F20170527220151fi.html&d=weW6yIUZoGcZx37EmzOfSmowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=0ff9e0d4\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170527/20170527220151fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"358a487b0d4f4f3066188d511cd87d67bd834841","tid":260727,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T23:49:22.000Z","msg":"官網SPEC<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.kodak.com/US/en/consumer/Product/Product_Specs/?contentId=4294998620&amp;TaxId=4294970150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.kodak.com%2FUS%2Fen%2Fconsumer%2FProduct%2FProduct_Specs%2F%3FcontentId%3D4294998620%26TaxId%3D4294970150&d=weW6yIUZoG